- get loose reminders into the inbox: notebooks, emails, scribbles

- process notes from meetings, conversations, emails
    - look for actions, projects, waiting-fors, calendar events, somedays, references

- review previous 2 weeks of calendar
    - look for remaining actions, references, follow up on waiting-fors. Get dangling items into the system. 

- review future 2 weeks of calendar
    - look for preparations that need to be completed. 

- mind dump
    - write down actions, new projects, waiting-fors, somedays, etc that aren't in the system

- review each project
    - update completed actions, waiting-fors
    - identify the next action

- review checklists

- review somedays


